{"word":"κάθημαι","slug":"κάθημαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰάϑημαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, ἧμαι</el> ‘sit’] ‘be at rest on the haunches’ <b>sit (down), take a seat <a href='B:470 4:16'>Mt 4:16</a>; <a href='B:470 13:1'>13:1f</a>; <a href='B:470 26:58'>26:58</a>; <a href='B:470 27:19'>27:19</a>; <a href='B:480 3:32'>Mk 3:32</a>; <a href='B:490 20:42'>Lk 20:42</a>; <a href='B:500 9:8'>J 9:8</a>; <a href='B:510 23:3'>Ac 23:3</a>; <a href='B:530 14:30'>1 Cor 14:30</a>; <a href='B:580 3:1'>Col 3:1</a>; <a href='B:660 2:3'>Js 2:3</a>; <a href='B:730 4:2'>Rv 4:2</a>; <a href='B:730 17:3'>17:3</a>; <a href='B:730 19:19'>19:19</a>.</b> The component of rest or leisure dominates in <b>14:6</b> (<el>ϰ.</el> = dwell/live) and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> also <b><a href='B:490 1:79'>Lk 1:79</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:καθήκω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:καθημερινός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}